@econsarahreber @tweeterbull @adamdavidson @susannecraig @russbuettner @mmcintire One misnomer about property is you cannot increase the fair value of real estate, land, buildings through fair market value. Fixed Assets are carried at the LOWER of cost or market value. They only get stepped up if a sale occurs.

@econsarahreber @tweeterbull @adamdavidson @susannecraig @russbuettner @mmcintire The easiest answer -

1) Company increases cash balance through loans/capital raise
2) Fraudulently capitalizes expenses or falsified vendors as property to increase total assets. 

I have had a few clients we have identified fraud in this manner while performing audits.
